To Install FastCat You Must Using Kitty Terminal Run sudo pacman -S kitty Then remove konsole gnome-console xterm xfce terminal or other terminal with sudo pacman -R

1 Open Kitty
2 Run doas pacman -S git (If You Havent Install git)
3 Run git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/m3tozz/FastCat.git && cd FastCat && bash ./fastcat.sh --shell
4 Type 01 Then 05
5 Run doas nano ~/.config/fastfetch/config.jsonc Then Change "source": "arch_small", // search for logos: fastfetch --list-logos or --print-logos To "source": "/usr/share/pixmaps/triaxis-logo.png",
6 Save With ctrl x y enter
7 Run doas nano ~/.bashrc then Add this line at the end fastfetch
8 Save With ctrl x y enter

Have Fun And You Can Use Or Rice Triaxis GNU/Linux With FastCat With Kitty Terminal

If There Is Any Mistakes You Can Go To https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux/issues/1 And Will Repair It
